  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/hiddriverkit\/digitizer-enum\ncrawled: 2026-03-11T06:47:35Z\n---\n\n# Digitizer\n\n**API Collection**\n\nUsages for digitizer devices, such as styluses and touch screens.\n\n## Getting the Usages\n\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_3DDigitizer**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Altitude**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Armature**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ArticulatedArm**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Azimuth**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_BarrelPressure**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_BarrelSwitch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_BatteryStrength**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_CapacitiveHeatMapDigitizer**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_CapacitiveHeatMapFrameData**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_CapacitiveHeatMapProtocolVendorID**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_CapacitiveHeatMapProtocolVersion**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ContactCount**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ContactCountMaximum**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ContactIdentifier**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_CoordinateMeasuringMachine**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_DataValid**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_DeviceConfiguration**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_DeviceIdentifier**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_DeviceMode**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_DeviceSettings**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Digitizer**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Eraser**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Finger**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_FreeSpaceWand**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacter**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterData**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterDataLength**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEnable**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncoding**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncodingUTF16BE**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncodingUTF16LE**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncodingUTF32BE**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncodingUTF32LE**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterEncodingUTF8**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_GestureCharacterQuality**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Height**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_InRange**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Invert**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_LightPen**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_MultiplePointDigitizer**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Pen**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ProgramChangeKeys**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Puck**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Quality**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_RelativeScanTime**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_ReportRate**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Reserved**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_SecondaryTipSwitch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_StereoPlotter**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_SurfaceSwitch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Stylus**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TabletFunctionKeys**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TabletPick**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Tap**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TipPressure**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TipSwitch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Touch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TouchPad**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TouchScreen**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TouchValid**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_TransducerIndex**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Twist**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Untouch**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_WhiteBoard**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_Width**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_XTilt**\n- **kHIDUsage_Dig_YTilt**\n\n## Devices\n\n- **Generic Device Controls**: Usages associated with generic types of device information, such as battery level.\n- **Keyboard or Keypad**: Usages related to keyboard and keypad devices.\n- **LEDs**: Usages related to the LEDs and other indicators on the device.\n- **Buttons**: Usages for devices that contain user-selectable controls.\n- **Ordinals**: Usages for custom-defined behaviors on a device.\n- **Telephony**: Usages for telephony devices, including telephone keypads and answering machines.\n- **Consumer**: Usages for app-specific controls on consumer devices, such as clocks, TVs, and audio equipment.\n- **Physical Interface Device**: Usages for devices with actuators or other physical interfaces.\n- **Alphanumeric Display**: Usages for alphanumeric displays on consumer devices.\n- **Haptics**\n- **FIDO**\n- **Braille Device**\n\n",
